1. The game must have movement, forward, backward, left, and right. Movement is in a one grid motion.
2. The game must have a road way obstacle with moving vehicles for the player to dodge.
3. The game must have a river in which the player must jump on moving obstacles to dodge the water.
4. The game must have "checkpoints." The checkpoints are just long grid strips with no obstacles.
5. The game must have a timer to track the current duration of the round.
6. The game must have name logging at the end for leaderboards.
7. The game must have an infinite number of runs so the player can build up a high score.
8. The game must have 3 lives, if they hit an obstacle they lose a life.
9. The game must have powerups such as quicker movement (2 grids at a time), frozen obstacles...
10. The game must be 3D.
